column5: I need a hand digging up an old thread from a few years back.  I’ve tried, but I can seem to find it.  It was a video of a guy singing a song.  He was super happy in the video.  Eastern European guy.  Smiles from ear to ear.  I don’t think there where lyrics, just this guy humming, or yodeling.  Whatever he was singing, he was so friggen happy when he was doing it.  One of my friends is going through a tough time, and I thought this video would cheer her up.  If anyone knows where to find this video, can you post a link?
No.  But that's hillarious..  I think the video I'm looking for is from a long time ago.  80's maybe?  The guys on stage.  Profesional video.

This isn't what you are looking for, but I laugh right out loud whenever I see this drummer!!   <iframe width="420" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/ItZyaOlrb7E" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
That's the one!!  Thanks very much man
That's a great Video!  I had to stop watching it once the drummer started really givin'er.  I'm at work, and don't want to bust a gut laughing!!
This guy takes lip synching to a new level.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PL8CD8PjVmA&feature=related  The guy is still doing it!
Thats our ole long time OFC pal ,Pigeonfisher.
Mr. Trololo (Eduard Khil) actually just passed away last week.  RIP Mr. Trololo.  How about the World's Happiest DJ???  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s7H7p80kZN8
